gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Pelicans 115, Knicks 92
gameRecap.excerpt: New Orleans defeats New York, 115-92. For New Orleans, Trey Murphy III led the way with 26 points (six 3PM), seven rebounds, and four assists while Brandon Ingram added 24 points, six rebounds, and five assists in the win. Donte DiVincenzo led the way with 23 points, four rebounds, and two steals aided by Bojan Bogdanovic tallying 20 points, four rebounds, five assists for New York in the losing effort. New Orleans wins and improves to 35-24, while New York moves to 35-24 in the loss.
